{"tid":967760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲男偷爬窗進房　性侵他82歲祖母　","createTime":"2019-01-03T18:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T03:25:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d661cd3a8104028b3e6c51f47d6a4e8bd7bf2676","tid":967760,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T18:15:26.000Z","msg":"一名男子性侵他82歲祖母，遭到警方逮捕。<br />\n據南非《Eyewitness News》，1月1日凌晨，南非杜蒂瓦(Dutywa)一處村莊，一名20歲男子性侵了他82歲的祖母，警方發言人馬納塔(Jackson Manatha)指出，這位祖母因為看到加害人從窗戶爬進來，所以認出加害人是她的孫子。<br />\n該名男子將於當地時間1月3日在杜蒂瓦地方法院出庭，罪名是強姦罪，巴特沃斯地區(Butterworth)指揮官薩卡福(Ngangema Xakavu)也強力指責性侵老人的行為，何況對方還是自己的祖母。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YCUxXGg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYCUxXGg.png&h=8b1eea04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5032f73847ab72a935ea9b6bd9fdb9380fcc360","tid":967760,"uid":135986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T18:17:07.000Z","msg":"棋靈王"},{"pid":"dd71d110c377c3166e08df6c376ad77a98ead712","tid":967760,"uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T18:18:01.000Z","msg":"行撚開 唔好再"},{"pid":"5f95d870c9ff039cf72f3e8064a7099aa26b58dc","tid":967760,"uid":157765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T18:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f6ca74df6e594eed554c2cb85d668d320e255b","tid":967760,"uid":115347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T18:21:29.000Z","msg":"少女唔鋤愛呀婆"},{"pid":"f5f73f78017f6d030a35ef4838cc9e66259fe5e5","tid":967760,"uid":109117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd71d110c377c3166e08df6c376ad77a98ead712","tid":967760,"uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T18:18:01.000Z","msg":"行撚開 唔好再"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T18:24:53.000Z","msg":"亂咁擺"},{"pid":"345edc36f075a3d8df71c456790d9bb7c7905eef","tid":967760,"uid":165510,"like":3,"dislike